Customer Use Cases:
    -Login/Register:
        -Create an account or login to save history and preferences
    -Search/Browse Movies:
        -Search movies by city, genre, language, date
    -View Movie Details:
        -view movie description, genre, ratings, release date, etc
    -View Shows:
        -View available showtimes for a movie
    -Select Seats:
        -Pick one or more available seats for a specific show
    -Book Tickets:
        -Confirm selection and proceed to payment
    -Cancel Booking:
        -Cancel an active booking
    -View Booking History:
        -See past and upcoming tickets with their status
    -Make Payment:
        -Complete transaction using payment options (UPI, Card, NetBanking, Wallet)

Admin Use Cases:
    -Manage Theaters:
        -Add/Edit theaters, cinema halls, seat layouts
    -Manage Shows:
        -Add/Edit shows (Change time, Cancel show) 
    -Manage Movies:
        -Add new movie, Update movie details, Delete movie
    -Manage Pricing:
        -Set price for a specific show or seat type
    -Manage User:
        -Block/Unblock users for certain violations.
